Body: I was wondering, if there a free or paid app that enables a user to view the entire GPS location history of the android internal GPS file without rooting the phone? Could such an app, assuming it exists, also enable one to back this GPS history up as well as to do same for any real-time GPS information?I just bought my android on Nov 2015 and, as you can tell by the form of my question, I do not know much about these phones?
Title: Location cache viewer and logger of the android internal gps
